#: ../../tips_and_tricks/shooting_tips/shooting_with_your_DSLR.rst:130
msgid ""
"The Nikon D90 was the first DSLR offering video: 720/24p (:abbr:`AVI (Audio "
"Video Interleave)` container)."
msgstr ""
"Nikon D90 je bil prvi aparat DSLR, ki je ponujal video: 720/24p (v vsebniku :"
"abbr:`AVI (Audio Video Interleave)`)."

#: ../../tips_and_tricks/shooting_tips/shooting_with_your_DSLR.rst:132
msgid ""
"D90 videos at 720p are scaled awfully. That is why you can see stair-"
"stepping in sharp, skew lines. If this becomes perturbing for a clip, you "
"can apply the :doc:`/effects_and_filters/video_effects/utility/"
"nikon_d90_stairstepping_fix` filter. Written (but not invented) by the "
"original author *Granjow*. See our |nikon-d90| for an example of how "
"stairstepping looks like (before and after correction)."
msgstr ""
"Videoposnetki D90 pri ločljivosti 720p so grozno pomanjšani. Zato lahko "
"vidite stopničasto spreminjanje v ostrih, poševnih linijah. Če to pri "
"posnetku postane moteče, lahko uporabite filter :doc:`/effects_and_filters/"
"video_effects/utility/nikon_d90_stairstepping_fix`. Napisal (vendar ne "
"izumil) ga je prvotni avtor *Granjow*. Oglejte si naš |nikon-d90| za primer, "
"kako je videti stopničasto spreminjanje (pred in po popravku)."

#: ../../tips_and_tricks/shooting_tips/shooting_with_your_DSLR.rst:134
